<h3>Usage</h3>

<p>To use these colors in your CSS, reference the CSS variables:</p>

<div class="component-demo-code">
  <pre><code class="language-css">.my-element {
  color: var(--color-primary);
  background-color: var(--color-background);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
}</code></pre>
</div>

<p>For consistency, always use the CSS variables instead of hardcoding color values. This ensures that if the color palette changes, your components will automatically update.</p> 